00:10:10.850 --> 00:10:14.569
do if you are going to rendezvous in space,
for example.

00:10:14.569 --> 00:10:18.990
But there are many other considerations that
you run into in the real world.

00:10:18.990 --> 00:10:22.430
So I am going to talk today mostly about Mission
