00:10:25.980 --> 00:10:32.980
And these I am short of so, please, people
in the class only as my handout for the slides

00:10:36.110 --> 00:10:39.119
here today.

00:10:39.119 --> 00:10:42.119
And the slides will be posted on the Web as
well.

00:10:42.119 --> 00:10:43.119
Yes.

00:10:43.119 --> 00:10:43.680
Dr.

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:46.939
Hoffman has got them off my electronics here.

00:10:46.939 --> 00:10:51.249
OK, so the things I am going to talk about
today basically are outlines on this page.

00:10:51.249 --> 00:10:52.509
We have a Mission Control.

00:10:52.509 --> 00:10:55.740
Here are some of the reasons we are going
to talk about trajectory.

00:10:55.740 --> 00:10:59.259
Planning and monitoring flight planning.

00:10:59.259 --> 00:10:59.949
Systems engineering.

00:10:59.949 --> 00:11:02.360
And then I've got a couple of stories from
the trenches.

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:07.800
And then I promise you no differential equations
